Start Plotter
===================================

$ cd plotter
$ docker build -t burst/plotter .
$ docker run -v /mnt/2tb_burst/:/tmp/plot_partition -it burst/plotter 
$ /omdcct/plot -k 7431686757998437789 -x 1 -d /tmp/plot_partition/ -n 4000000 -m 24000

/mnt/2tb_burst is host partition mount point
-k is account number to give rewards to
-x is the CPU type
-n number of blocks (256kB each)
-m step size (RAM to use)



Start Miner
===================================

$ cd miner
$ docker build -t burst/miner .
$ docker run -p 8080:80 burst/miner

Server will be available on http://localhost:8080

